Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳… 聴力を賭けたＥカード
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:54.30,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's sense of hearing is\Nbeing gambled in E-Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:58.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３戦 ４戦と利根川に連敗のカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:58.80,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji lost the 3rd and 4th\Ngame to Tonegawa in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,針は進む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.37,default,,0,0,0,,The needle inches\Ncloser everytime he loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:09.46,default,,0,0,0,,And now the 5th game.\NKaiji needs a victory badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:11.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５戦目…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:11.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝利への突破口が欲しいカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:12.14,default,,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:18.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　恐れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:17.94,default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:19.82,default,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:23.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一筋の光明…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.72,default,,0,0,0,,A streak of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:30.21,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Trifled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:35.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れ… それだけは利根川にも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:35.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対 あるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:35.08,default,,0,0,0,,Fear. It's something even\NTonegawa should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:37.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:36.94,default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for\Nhim to be fearless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜなら これはギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.53,default,,0,0,0,,Because we're gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:43.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルとは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:43.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リスクを背負うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:43.05,default,,0,0,0,,Gambling means risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れを抱くこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:44.95,default,,0,0,0,,And he has to fear losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:49.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はもちろん 利根川も必ず震える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:48.95,default,,0,0,0,,I fear and so will he!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いよいよとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れないはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.12,default,,0,0,0,,Truthfully, there's no way\Nanyone can avoid fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この心理戦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｅカードで突き詰めるべきは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:56.69,default,,0,0,0,,E-Card's a psychological game.\NI have to find the opponent's fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:59.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の恐れ 恐怖がどこにあるか…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.72,default,,0,0,0,,The question is...\N "how do i find out?".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:04.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つければ それが足がかりになる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:04.07,default,,0,0,0,,I've to find his fear.\NIt's easier to win that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし カイジには見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:06.76,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:10.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は あまりにも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:10.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つかみどころがない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:10.03,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa has too\Nfew weak spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば 作る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.71,default,,0,0,0,,Fine!\NI'll create them then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:18.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川の心に恐れの幻想を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:16.80,default,,0,0,0,,I'll create a fear illusion\Nin Tonegawa's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:20.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となると…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:19.72,default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:45.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれやれ　やっと決めたか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.52,default,,0,0,0,,At last, you've decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:49.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３分… ただ待つ３分は長いもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:46.86,default,,0,0,0,,3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.45,default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for 3 minutes\Nis quite long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君には あっという間でもな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.85,default,,0,0,0,,I know it seems\Nshort for you, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろいろ考えたのだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下手な考え 何とやらだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.08,default,,0,0,0,,I know you're \Ntrying to plan wisely,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.00,default,,0,0,0,,but it seems you're\Ngoing in the wrong direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:01.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｅカードは大筋の思考の流れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:01.23,default,,0,0,0,,In E-Card, it'll be alright\Nas long as the overall...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動きを間違えなければ それでよし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.68,default,,0,0,0,,...flow of thinking and\Nmovements aren't mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:06.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単な話さ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.62,default,,0,0,0,,It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 あっさり選択 提出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:10.20,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa chose and\Nplaced his card with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５戦目の２枚目 オープン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.76,default,,0,0,0,,The 2nd card of\Nthe 5th game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.92,default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは｢奴隷｣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.64,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's Slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４戦目と同じく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目に再び｢奴隷｣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:20.64,default,,0,0,0,,Like the 4th game,\Nhe chose Slave as the 2nd card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:28.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢市民｣　利根川の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.80,default,,0,0,0,,Citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:27.88,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa's win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 これで３連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.43,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa 3rd\Nstraight win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:40.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふ… それでは早速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.42,default,,0,0,0,,Alright then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.08,default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３連敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.72,default,,0,0,0,,3 straight losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:56.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か戦略を思いついたかに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:56.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みえたカイジだったが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:57.93,default,,0,0,0,,Any strategy Kaiji had,\Nfailed him it seemed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 負け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:01.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金は得られず ただ針だけが進む
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.65,default,,0,0,0,,Still no cash. But the\Nneedle's moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:04.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合計 14ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.77,default,,0,0,0,,A total of 14 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,徐々に暗雲… 暗雲立ちこめる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.18,default,,0,0,0,,The dark clouds gather...\NThey gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:12.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ　勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:12.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この人も負ける 利根川に…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.23,default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.\NHe can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:12.19,default,,0,0,0,,That guy will lose\Nto Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.20,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.19,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し希望を持たせつつ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つわけにはいかんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:19.64,default,,0,0,0,,Give him a little hope.\NBut make sure you still win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり寄せつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち方をすると
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:22.60,default,,0,0,0,,If you keep winning like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:27.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が ほれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:27.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安全にいってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:26.88,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji will opt\Nfor the safe route.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負を捨ててな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:29.07,default,,0,0,0,,He'll avoid going head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:32.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは それだけが心配でな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.28,default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried\Nthat will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.78,default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:38.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ様
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:38.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次のベット 賭け距離は？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.58,default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaiji, what is your next bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:41.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ様？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.02,default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.08,default,,0,0,0,,10.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:47.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.19,default,,0,0,0,,10!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:49.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は10いく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.09,default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:00.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゅ 10って… いいのか 本当に？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.89,default,,0,0,0,,10?! Are you serious?\N Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余計なことを言うではない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.61,default,,0,0,0,,Hey there,\Nwe don't need your input.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は黙って ただ書けばいいのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:07.27,default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet and\Nwrite it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の気が変わらぬうちにな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.28,default,,0,0,0,,Before Kaiji changes his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:11.61,default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.12,default,,0,0,0,,This is fun. Fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愉快 愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川が ここで10ミリ勝てば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:24.63,default,,0,0,0,,If Tonegawa wins,\NKaiji will lose 24 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの負けは24ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り試合 １ミリずつ張っても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.81,default,,0,0,0,,Even if he bets\N1 mm consecutively...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全敗すれば30ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.87,default,,0,0,0,,...and loses each time,\Nit will be 30mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:33.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破滅… 針が鼓膜を破る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.63,default,,0,0,0,,Destruction! The needle\Nwill pierce his eardrum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:39.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あはは… 面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:39.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう勝負をしてくれてこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:41.14,default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. I'm glad I stayed\Nfor this overtime game...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この延長戦 夜更かしにも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:45.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味があろうというもの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.65,default,,0,0,0,,...when you gamble like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:46.34,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.15,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:50.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は100パーセント 勝ちなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:51.15,default,,0,0,0,,Win the next game 100%.\NIt should be easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たやすかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.59,default,,0,0,0,,You have the advantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:54.44,default,,0,0,0,,...because you're on\Nthe Emperor side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,有利な皇帝側だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よもや負けなどしまい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.55,default,,0,0,0,,You can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.89,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな… 何でここで10ミリ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.40,default,,0,0,0,,No way. \NWhy 10 mm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ見込みの少ない奴隷側で…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.02,default,,0,0,0,,He's on the Slave side\Nwith no chance to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:08.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくしかなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.66,default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:08.48,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.90,default,,0,0,0,,He must do it now\Nto win big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここでいかないと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう大勝はないから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このＥカードで まとまった金を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,得ようとするならば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:16.09,default,,0,0,0,,In E-Card, to win big, one must\Nbet a large amount and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５倍返しの奴隷側で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,厚く張って勝たねばならない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:19.91,default,,0,0,0,,...win on the Slave side\Nwith 5 times the return rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:23.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジはラスト３戦は奴隷側だが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.68,default,,0,0,0,,Towards the end, Kaiji will\Nplay the Slave side again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時には厚く張る距離が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:27.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残っていないかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:27.42,default,,0,0,0,,And he might not have\Nmuch distance to bet then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:31.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となると まだ張れる距離が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:31.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残っているこの６戦が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:31.60,default,,0,0,0,,So while the needle is still\Na considerable length away,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:35.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷で厚く張るラストチャンス…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:35.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.61,default,,0,0,0,,it's his last chance to\Nbet on the Slave side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.91,default,,0,0,0,,He has to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:38.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムチャを承知でか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.28,default,,0,0,0,,So he knows what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.58,default,,0,0,0,,The 6th game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:44.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先出しは皇帝側の利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.21,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa plays first.\NHe's on the Emperor's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 初めて熟考
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.04,default,,0,0,0,,For the first time,\NTonegawa thinks hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動きが止まる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:48.80,default,,0,0,0,,He stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの気迫　会長の叱咤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:53.48,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's spirit. \NThe director's rebuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:57.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この６戦目の重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.98,default,,0,0,0,,The importance\Nof this 6th game!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ 利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.16,default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:04.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しびれたろ？この勝負で初めて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:04.49,default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid for the\Nfirst time, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,有利な皇帝側とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:08.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けられない勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.01,default,,0,0,0,,Even though winning\Nis your advantage now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.45,default,,0,0,0,,you can't lose just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:12.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けることを許されない勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.99,default,,0,0,0,,...because you're\Non the Emperor's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けることの恐れを 初めて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:16.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心中に感じる勝負なんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.79,default,,0,0,0,,For the first time now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:16.50,default,,0,0,0,,you can feel\Nthe fear of losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:21.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 提出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:21.54,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa, places his card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:31.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,６戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:31.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目のカード 出そろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:31.12,default,,0,0,0,,The first cards for\Nthe game are laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:39.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引き分け　｢市民｣と｢市民｣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:38.52,default,,0,0,0,,Draw.\NCitizen with Citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっ… そうだ　こうなる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.99,default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NThat's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:48.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れれば恐れるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:48.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人は無理をしない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:48.23,default,,0,0,0,,The more one feels fear,\Nthe less one goes all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,堅い戦略に流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.03,default,,0,0,0,,One would take\Na safer choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先出しで表情を観察される１枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:55.83,default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't play the Emperor\Nfor the 1st and 3rd key card...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:58.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして３枚目に勝負カード
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:58.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢皇帝｣は出してこない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.54,default,,0,0,0,,...because his opponent\Ncan see his expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出すとすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が先にカードを置く
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.76,default,,0,0,0,,He'll only do it\Nwhen it's my turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.04,default,,0,0,0,,...to deal for the\N2nd and 4th card first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目か４枚目…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:08.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし ２枚目はすでに殺した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:08.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,埋め込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.34,default,,0,0,0,,But I've already\Nkilled the 2nd card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.71,default,,0,0,0,,I've buried it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さい疑心という恐れ… 鬼を…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:11.55,default,,0,0,0,,...with fear\Nand suspicion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:16.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は２枚目に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:16.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢皇帝｣を通せない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.56,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa's not playing\NEmperor for the 2nd card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は４戦に続けて５戦も
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目に｢奴隷｣を出した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.86,default,,0,0,0,,For the 4th and 5th games,\NI played Slave for the 2nd card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目が｢奴隷｣という印象を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:27.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川に植え付けたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.54,default,,0,0,0,,I wanted him to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.40,default,,0,0,0,,...the impression that\Nthe 2nd card is a Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は恐れる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.78,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa is afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.34,default,,0,0,0,,He thinks I'll deal\N3 Slaves in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よもや３度 続けてと思いながらも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:38.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしかしたらという気持ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:38.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,拭えない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.41,default,,0,0,0,,...but there might\Nbe something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:42.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひたすら考え
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:42.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川が出す結論は｢保留｣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:42.57,default,,0,0,0,,He'll consider it properly and\Nhe'll resolved to being reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:47.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目には
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:47.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 ｢市民｣を出し 様子見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.92,default,,0,0,0,,He'll deal the Citizen again\Nfor the 2nd card, as a gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一か八かなどしない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや できないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:48.97,default,,0,0,0,,He won't take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.00,default,,0,0,0,,No, he can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:55.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなれば３枚目は 先出しで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:55.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢皇帝｣は切りがたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.72,default,,0,0,0,,It'll be difficult\Nto play Emperor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.37,default,,0,0,0,,...as the 3rd card later\Nwhen he deals 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は４枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.93,default,,0,0,0,,The deciding card will\Nthen come in the 4th card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:02.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 考え続け
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:02.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４分になろうかという時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.10,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa contemplates...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.50,default,,0,0,0,,And just before\N4 minutes passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:06.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっと選択
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.47,default,,0,0,0,,he finally chooses his card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,提出　カード 出そろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:09.46,default,,0,0,0,,He places it! \NBoth cards are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで勝てば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほぼ勝てる｢皇帝｣を３戦残し
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.24,default,,0,0,0,,If he wins now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.86,default,,0,0,0,,and wins the remaining\Nthree games on the Emperor side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち金の合計も700万！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.10,default,,0,0,0,,he'll gain a\Ntotal of 7 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:23.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万とはいわないが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:23.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万は完全に視野に…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:23.02,default,,0,0,0,,20 million is too far fetched\Nbut 10 million is within reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝て　勝って道を…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:27.56,default,,0,0,0,,Win this! And open the\Nway to a great victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大勝の道を開け！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:36.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは｢市民｣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.27,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji chose Citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:46.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ？市民だろ お前も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:45.70,default,,0,0,0,,Well? You've chosen\NCitizen too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.51,default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:53.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君 実によく分かるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.72,default,,0,0,0,,I know you well, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私には君が何を考え
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その｢市民｣に至ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:57.52,default,,0,0,0,,I know what was on your mind\Nwhen you picked Citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして それはほぼ正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.03,default,,0,0,0,,I must say that\Nyou were almost right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:04.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このＥカードにおける
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:04.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,定石のような考えかもしれぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.82,default,,0,0,0,,You almost grasped the formula\Nto this game of E-Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:07.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 残念ながら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.02,default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その定石という地点が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルでは最も浅はかなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:12.30,default,,0,0,0,,That formula is the last\Nthing you need in a gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:20.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 ２枚目に｢皇帝｣を通す
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.52,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa played Emperor\Nfor his 2nd card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ… バカな… どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.61,default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２枚目に｢皇帝｣は通せない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通せないはずなのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.55,default,,0,0,0,,He can't play Emperor\Nfor the 2nd card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.05,default,,0,0,0,,I was certain it was\Nimpossible, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.90,default,,0,0,0,,Then... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では ゴー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:05.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このＥカードに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:05.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必勝法のようなものはない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.98,default,,0,0,0,,There's no sure-win\Nstrategy in E-Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:09.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるとすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:09.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ確率を高める何かだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:09.09,default,,0,0,0,,Learning the chances\Nof winning in E-Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは一朝一夕で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たどり着くようなものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:12.82,default,,0,0,0,,...is not something\Nyou can learn in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:18.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓄積なのだ　長年の経験のな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.24,default,,0,0,0,,It is all about\Nyears of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし ビギナーは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐそれを手にしようとする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:21.45,default,,0,0,0,,However, beginners always\Nfail to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや つかんだような気になり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,掲げたがるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:25.39,default,,0,0,0,,They assume that they've\Nunderstood the game well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確信めいたものを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:27.02,default,,0,0,0,,So full of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな確信は付け焼き刃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:33.86,default,,0,0,0,,Full of confidence, they simply\Nspring at the first opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 本人にとっては
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大変なひらめきに感じられ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:36.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっさり それに沿おうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.62,default,,0,0,0,,...without much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:40.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,疑い続けること…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:40.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不安であり続けることが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:40.66,default,,0,0,0,,To have doubts and to\Nbe alert at all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルで生き残るために
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最も必要な心構えなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:44.63,default,,0,0,0,,...is the most important\Nquality in gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:48.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,素人ほど すぐそれを捨てる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.80,default,,0,0,0,,But amateurs forgo these details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:51.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が考えて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:51.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たどり着いた地点は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.10,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, the level\Nwhich you've reached...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだまだ理屈の領域にすぎん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.48,default,,0,0,0,,...is still within\Nthe realm of logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:57.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それではダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:57.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肝心なのはその先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.84,default,,0,0,0,,That's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.11,default,,0,0,0,,The next step would be\Ncrossing over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:12:00.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理屈の上に乗って うごめく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:12:00.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いの感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:12:00.38,default,,0,0,0,,...and reading\Nyour opponent's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:03.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:03.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:01.88,default,,0,0,0,,Feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.25,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君は理屈で止まり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:07.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感情へは踏み込まない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.64,default,,0,0,0,,You stopped at logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:07.70,default,,0,0,0,,You did not step into\Nthe realm of feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:11.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは勝てぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:11.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:11.09,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you\Ncan win like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:15.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に こちらから見た
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:15.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の感情は丸見えだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:15.12,default,,0,0,0,,Your emotions are\Ncrystal clear to me, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽すぎる勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.28,default,,0,0,0,,This is too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:19.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 唯一 苦労した点といえば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.96,default,,0,0,0,,If I may add,\Nmy greatest challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:22.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が私に期待する反応を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.90,default,,0,0,0,,...is not to show the expression\Nyou expect from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つつがなくして見せることくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:29.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 悩んでいるふりを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:29.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,することに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:29.02,default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I had to\Nput on a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正直 一番骨を折った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.37,default,,0,0,0,,I had to act as if I'm\Nthinking properly to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:45.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ ６戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:45.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10ミリの負けにより
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:47.52,default,,0,0,0,,In the 6th game, Kaiji lost 10mm,\Nmaking it a total of 24 mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,針の合計は24ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:51.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鼓膜までの猶予 ６ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:51.26,default,,0,0,0,,He has 6 mm left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:55.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして残り６試合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:54.69,default,,0,0,0,,And exactly 6 games left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:58.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと６ミリ　６戦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:58.11,default,,0,0,0,,6 more mm\Nand 6 games left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次のベット 賭けの距離は？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:04.20,default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaiji,\Nwhat's your next bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:11.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.84,default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.68,default,,0,0,0,,1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:16.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？おいおい よせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.23,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の最低の針の距離は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２だったんじゃないのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.42,default,,0,0,0,,I thought your\Nminimum bet was 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんのちょっと前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の忠告を無視して
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:23.42,default,,0,0,0,,Just a while ago, you\Nignored people's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:27.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２張っておいて もう降参か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.28,default,,0,0,0,,Now you're giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:30.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメなのか やっぱり…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.82,default,,0,0,0,,Now it's really hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふ… まあいい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が１だと言うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:34.86,default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay.\NWe'll respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは尊重せんとな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.79,default,,0,0,0,,If you insist,\Nthen 1 it shall be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.97,default,,0,0,0,,- Hey. \N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では 続けるか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.16,default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:47.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度はカイジ君が皇帝側
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.72,default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn\Nto be the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.50,default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:56.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えてやろうか １つだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.97,default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:14:00.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜカイジ君が敗れ 私が勝つか…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:59.90,default,,0,0,0,,...why you will lose\Nand I will win, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このＥカードは心理戦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.30,default,,0,0,0,,E-Card is a\Npsychological game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:08.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうカイジ君は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:08.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えているようだが 実は違う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:07.63,default,,0,0,0,,In reality, it's very different\Nfrom what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:11.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことより
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:11.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はるかに勝利に近づく道がある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:11.66,default,,0,0,0,,There's a faster method to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは見る力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:15.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見る？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.86,default,,0,0,0,,And that is the ability to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.14,default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:18.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手が動揺しているかどうかを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:18.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:20.34,default,,0,0,0,,How to see through\Nyour opponent's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:22.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単純で直接的な人を観察する能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.41,default,,0,0,0,,Simply put, the power\Nto observe others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:26.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 皇帝側は｢皇帝｣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:26.16,default,,0,0,0,,Which means, Emperor\Nin the Emperor side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:29.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷側は｢奴隷｣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.65,default,,0,0,0,,Slave in Slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:32.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負カードを出した時の
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:32.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の心の震えを
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:33.64,default,,0,0,0,,To win, you have to \Nread the opponent's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:36.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,観察する力が問われている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:35.42,default,,0,0,0,,...at the moment of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふ… ｢何をバカなことを｣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:39.34,default,,0,0,0,,"What on earth\Nare you talking about?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:42.43,default,,0,0,0,,"If that were possible,\Nit'd be too easy."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢それができれば苦労しない｣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って顔だな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:47.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ところが経験を積めば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:47.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それほど難しいことではない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.86,default,,0,0,0,,That's what it says on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.10,default,,0,0,0,,But in fact, it's not difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:51.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例えばカイジ君の場合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:51.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負カードを出す時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.78,default,,0,0,0,,For example, Kaiji,\Nin your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:54.44,default,,0,0,0,,you stoop forward slightly\Nwhen playing a key card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通常より若干 前傾が深くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:15:01.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに出した後の目線の動き
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:15:01.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残したカードの持ち方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.48,default,,0,0,0,,After you've decided,\Nyour eye movement,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.78,default,,0,0,0,,your style of holding\Nyour remaining cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,首の据わり 口元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.68,default,,0,0,0,,your neck position,\Nthe shape of your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,眉の表情 肩 ひじ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:06.48,default,,0,0,0,,the arch of your brows,\Nyour shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.46,default,,0,0,0,,elbows and\Nmany other areas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかにも いくらでもあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要するに告白しているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.07,default,,0,0,0,,They speak \Nlike a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:15.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,口に出さねど体中で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.43,default,,0,0,0,,Your body language\Nsays it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:20.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠しきれない　感情は決して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:20.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠しきれるものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:20.02,default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for you to hide\Nyour emotions in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人というのは感情の器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.44,default,,0,0,0,,Humans are containers\N for emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常に満々とした水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.18,default,,0,0,0,,They filled up to\Nthe brim like water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆらゆらとした感情を
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たたえている
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:33.83,default,,0,0,0,,That emotion will spill with\Na slight movement of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:32.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その感情は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:32.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとした心の動きで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たやすく あふれる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:38.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,器が小さいほど いびつなほど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:38.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感情はあふれやすい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:38.36,default,,0,0,0,,In a person of lower calibre,\Nit would spill out faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてそれは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐに どうにかなるものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.92,default,,0,0,0,,And it's not something\Nyou can rectify immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,経験が必要なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.37,default,,0,0,0,,Experience is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一朝一夕で感情は隠せん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.31,default,,0,0,0,,You can't hide your\Nfeelings in a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:51.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よって カイジ君は勝ち得ない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.43,default,,0,0,0,,So you're bound\Nto lose, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな… もしそうなら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が先にカードを出す時は全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.34,default,,0,0,0,,No way. If that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.88,default,,0,0,0,,then I've have lost everything\Nwhen I started first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:16:00.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべて看破されるって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:16:00.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ことじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:59.51,default,,0,0,0,,He'd have\Nseen through everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.84,default,,0,0,0,,Don't take me for a fool!\NThat's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:05.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなわけない　あるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:08.15,default,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous.\NHe's bluffing. It's his strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:08.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはヤツのハッタリ 戦略…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:10.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だまされるな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.14,default,,0,0,0,,I'm not falling for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.92,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:24.80,default,,0,0,0,,In the 7th game,\NKaiji played the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:25.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７戦目　カイジ あえて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:25.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目に｢皇帝｣を提出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.25,default,,0,0,0,,Well? Try reading this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうだ　見抜いてみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.54,default,,0,0,0,,If you can, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見抜けるものなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:36.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし利根川 あっさり提出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.22,default,,0,0,0,,But Tonegawa played calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 ｢奴隷｣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:43.50,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa, Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.32,default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he saw through\NKaiji's plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの考えを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見透かしたかのように…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:55.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 皇帝側でも勝てず５連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:53.02,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji lost on\Nthe Emperor side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.03,default,,0,0,0,,5 straight losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:03.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,８戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:03.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また１ミリ張っての８戦目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.68,default,,0,0,0,,The 8th game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.87,default,,0,0,0,,The 8th game with yet\Nanother wager of 1 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:08.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな　バカな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:08.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなことってあるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.77,default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.79,default,,0,0,0,,Such things don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてこんなことが？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.81,default,,0,0,0,,How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:12.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや完全に疑心暗鬼のカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:13.10,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is full of suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:16.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となれば そう簡単に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:16.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢皇帝｣は通せない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:16.44,default,,0,0,0,,He was unable to\Nplay the Emperor card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚目　２枚目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:21.32,default,,0,0,0,,1st card, 2nd card, 3rd card...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:24.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３枚目　｢市民｣を出して引き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:24.10,default,,0,0,0,,All Citizens and draws.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:28.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４枚目　二者択一の勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.22,default,,0,0,0,,4th card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:30.02,default,,0,0,0,,He's left with one\Nout of 2 choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:31.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,追い詰められる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何てこと… この状況は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.16,default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:37.83,default,,0,0,0,,I planned to trap\NTonegawa like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が利根川に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,してやりたかったのに 逆…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.05,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:47.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 利根川　共に｢市民｣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:46.34,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and Tonegawa\N both dealt Citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,４枚目も引き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:49.26,default,,0,0,0,,All four cards were draws.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るカードは カイジ ｢皇帝｣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.44,default,,0,0,0,,The cards remaining:\N Kaiji has Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:54.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 ｢奴隷｣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.85,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa has Slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:57.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりカードを出すまでもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.25,default,,0,0,0,,There's no need\Nto reveal the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川の勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:58.94,default,,0,0,0,,It is Tonegawa's win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:07.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 本来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:07.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的に有利な皇帝側でも負け
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:06.56,default,,0,0,0,,Being on the Emperor Side\Ndidn't benefit Kaiji at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:11.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,泥沼　６連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:10.23,default,,0,0,0,,Burdened with 6 straight losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念のために言っておこう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.24,default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to remind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし それを外そうとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:21.58,default,,0,0,0,,The metalwork is special.\NYou won't succeed in removing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:22.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念ながら その金具は特殊でな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特別の工具で分解する以外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外す すべはない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:25.84,default,,0,0,0,,You need special\Nequipment to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強引に外そうとした場合は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:29.98,default,,0,0,0,,If you try removing it\Nby force,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このリモコンのアラームが鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.22,default,,0,0,0,,the alarm will go\Noff in this remote control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:37.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外させんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:37.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらからすれば その耳は人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.39,default,,0,0,0,,And it'd alert us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.39,default,,0,0,0,,That ear is a\Nhostage for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:42.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝手はさせん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:42.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は貸してやっているだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.14,default,,0,0,0,,You can't do as\Nyou please with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.76,default,,0,0,0,,We're only lending\Nit to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負がつけば その聴力は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:46.86,default,,0,0,0,,Once the match ends,\Nthat ear is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頂く
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.27,default,,0,0,0,,Drill, drill, drill...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:59.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残すは４戦　そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.42,default,,0,0,0,,4 games remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:58.79,default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:02.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鼓膜までの猶予も４ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.28,default,,0,0,0,,4 mm before reaching\Nthe ear drum!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメ… 疑いようもない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.20,default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうこれは偶然でも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッタリでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:08.46,default,,0,0,0,,This is neither a\Ncoincidence nor a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:13.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男は本当に分かるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.93,default,,0,0,0,,This guy really knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:17.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の出したカードが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:17.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負カードか否か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:16.23,default,,0,0,0,,...whether I'm playing\Nthe key card or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異能… 異能の観察眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.31,default,,0,0,0,,Extraordinary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.30,default,,0,0,0,,An extraordinary \Npower of observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:24.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさに悪魔だ　悪魔じみている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.80,default,,0,0,0,,He's like a devil. \NJust like a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの的中率は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:28.91,default,,0,0,0,,That level of observation is\Nbeyond human ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:30.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とっくに人間の域を超えている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:35.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の心の震え 動揺を見抜く天才…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.81,default,,0,0,0,,He's a genius. \NHe can see people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:38.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.47,default,,0,0,0,,A devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とてもかなわない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見透かされる　すべて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.44,default,,0,0,0,,I can't beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.43,default,,0,0,0,,He sees everything clearly.\N Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:46.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の心はすべて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.26,default,,0,0,0,,My mind... Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:50.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てない　勝てるわけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:49.62,default,,0,0,0,,I can't win!\NIt's impossible to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が唯一 勝てる可能性があるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:54.77,default,,0,0,0,,Winning the last game as\NEmperor is my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝側の最終戦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次の９戦目だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.57,default,,0,0,0,,The 9th game next.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９戦目を負けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,針は間違いなく４ミリ進む
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:01.94,default,,0,0,0,,If he loses the 9th game,\Nthe needle will extend 4mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合計 30ミリ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.12,default,,0,0,0,,A total of 30 mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:06.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鼓膜に至る！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:05.58,default,,0,0,0,,It's reaching his eardrum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっとるな　ここだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:14.29,default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?\NIt's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここを勝ちさえすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは問題なくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:17.59,default,,0,0,0,,If you win here,\Nthere'll be no problems later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気を緩めるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.98,default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:22.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっております
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.59,default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:25.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく夜更かしをしてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.45,default,,0,0,0,,I stayed up\Nall night for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:31.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで来たら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:31.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜひ カイジ君の絶叫を聞きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:30.20,default,,0,0,0,,Since we're here,\NI want to hear Kaiji's screams!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:34.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも その声も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:34.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の耳には
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:34.14,default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, the scream will only
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:37.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,半分しか届かないだろうがな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.75,default,,0,0,0,,reach half of Kaiji's ears though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:53.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,９戦目　カイジが皇帝側で戦う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:53.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の試合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:52.86,default,,0,0,0,,The 9th game. The last\Nround Kaiji plays as Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは勝ちがたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷側だけが残る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.03,default,,0,0,0,,He's left with playing on\Nthe Slave side after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:21:02.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この１戦 勝つか負けるかで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:21:02.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天国と地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:01.73,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's fate hangs upon\Nthe win or loss of this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:05.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば生き残り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:05.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ければ破滅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.67,default,,0,0,0,,Win and survive.\N Lose and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破壊する
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.84,default,,0,0,0,,Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:12.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずか１ミリでも届けば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:12.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,器官を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:12.47,default,,0,0,0,,If it reaches even 1 mm closer,\N the eardrum gets destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突破口を見いだせるか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:19.70,default,,0,0,0,,Will Kaiji find a solution?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:46.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回 ｢限界｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:45.60,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Limit.
